{"tid":5893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個無堅持玩落去既野。後悔中","createTime":"2016-11-27T06:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T03:55:24.000Z","uid":21110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4decaaa6d3f2714b24d48fd72a7f07ed4199e718","tid":5893,"uid":21110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"曾經小學學左三年羽毛球，到中學無呢個學會，就無再打<br />\n如果有打落去應該港隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26e4e23cb5dfc8a1a7687a5156c63b004312272","tid":5893,"uid":9142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"水球，香港少人打keep住玩就港隊，當時有朋友一開始仲廢過自己，一直打就打到參加亞運"},{"pid":"0b94bbec7e92f53ab9505dee2385e4e168327a65","tid":5893,"uid":22197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:25:08.000Z","msg":"鋼琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個比屋企人逼練琴仲要我錄低自己練琴過程搞到我好唔開心放棄學琴<br />\n而家好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得彈琴好靚 教琴又好搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f556fa0adb1b60386ebeeb77f648bac470502448","tid":5893,"uid":8177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"田徑 傷完之後沒心機再練翻 太辛苦"},{"pid":"f7cb523b56e167a897f43107c886fa85db728595","tid":5893,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:27:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcfa5fc4866122e7f1933a0e0f8e4a2c44866944","tid":5893,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"小提琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 氣