T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"空手道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果陣嫌佢學黎學去都係果幾招 悶得濟唔再學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876684a7bf6a735dae547c3d1cb6a845831f7d80","tid":5893,"uid":4545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:19:14.000Z","msg":"花式跳繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48758acb3792de93f004ab18531991dfbc25e7b6","tid":5893,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"跟左個垃圾學琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23e95c9e1a7578c032129caf0b204905ad74c62","tid":5893,"uid":4031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:24:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56e2ebee90a02f307fc3a6e6e1bbfc680985aa58","tid":5893,"uid":6848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">魔術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學六年班嗰年生日老豆送左副啤牌<br />\n同埋一隻垃圾「魔術通」既碟比我<br />\n之後就開始自己上網自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到中學機緣巧合有個鬼佬亞sir叫我做下活動<br />\n同校長玩完之後，佢問我有無興趣搞個魔術學會<br />\n做埋創會主席，出去都有試過接過下街show<br />\n但中學完左之後，又要做野又要陪女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得翻無聊無野做嗰時先拎啲牌撚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住乜都唔洗憂興趣行頭既日子</span>"},{"pid":"d56487dc830d7150c13c7053aea1a625dd3d885c","tid":5893,"uid":6589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五歲開始跳左十年 皇家試仲有9字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但俾人杯葛頂唔順放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938e34516c96ec861ee77fe9